name: Gather Community Plant #023 - Stipinpixel
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from Tezos artists and their rendition of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Stipinpixel is an architect who has been creating some very unique works on Tezos including the "Street Moment" series. In this work we see a green gardener tending to plants.

"Sometimes it’s a form of expression, other times or maybe most of the time it’s as a way to investigate, decode and be able to understand a little more about my environment, human relationships." - stipinpixel
